	* gnome-dock-item.h: Change GNOME_DOCK_ITEM_BEH_NEVER_DETACH
	to GNOME_DOCK_ITEM_BEH_NEVER_FLOATING for Ettore; add
	GNOME_DOCK_ITEM_BEH_LOCKED.

