 	members to gboolean.  Removed 'number_of_interact_requests' and
 	replaced it with 'interaction_keys'. Member 'number_of_...'
  	renamed to 'save_yourself_emitted'. Made 'enviroment' of type
 	'GHashTable' instead of 'GList'.

